text: Sixten Johansson (25 January 1910 - 13 October 1991) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1991 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Boden Municipality
